cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on using deep learning for face detection, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and fine-tuning pre-trained models (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of multi-resolution approaches (cs.MM) and the development of state-of-the-art detectors (cs.NE).
